skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: super ego booster
des:
Say "Alexa, open Super Ego Booster" to begin your path down the road to a huge self-esteem boost! 

If you like the compliments, say "Again" or "Another" to keep indulging. 
Say "Help" to learn more about Super Ego Booster, including voice command reminders.

You also have the option to upgrade your ego message experience with premium Super Ego Boosters. The premium Super Ego Booster gives you more superior and personalized words of encouragement that will undoubtedly hype up your ego. 

You deserve it!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
